data.description: Welcome to this fully upgraded 3 bed 2 bath home converted to real property. With a NEW ROOF,  new vinyl and linoleum flooring, quartz countertops, custom cabinets, and a luxurious master bathroom, this home is a true gem. Step inside to discover a modern and inviting living area, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring quartz countertops and custom cabinets for all your culinary needs. The master bathroom offers a separate bath tub and shower, along with dual sinks for added convenience. Enjoy a spa-like experience every day. Situated on a 48,787 square-foot lot, this property provides over an acre of land to create your dream outdoor space. Embrace the privacy and freedom this generous lot size offers. Located in Pahrump, you'll enjoy a peaceful lifestyle while still being close to amenities. Don't miss out on this exceptional home. Schedule a showing today and envision yourself living in this remarkable property in Pahrump, Nevada.
